qrcode-generator-desc: QRCode Meika stap intanet app tu meik wanpela QRCode. Olso, givim sapotim tu putim on Wikimedia Commons.
pleaselogin: tu wanpela app wantaim MediaWiki akount bilong yupela tu putim wanpela QR Code on Wikimedia Commons!
enter-url: Taipim URL bilong eni peij bilong artikel bilong eni Wikimedia websait.
modify-details: Senis taitl na adim deskripsion long QR kod fail:
error: Samting go rong wail uplodin QR kod bilong yupela :-/
success: QR kod bilong yupela stap suksesfuli uploded tu Wikimedia Commons!
goto-home: Go bek tu peij bilong haus
